Properties.Caption: Просмотр разбора информации из расчетных документов
Properties.Tag: Select Convert(DateTime,Left([DOC].[CDOC],8)) As [Дата файла документов], Substring([DOC].[CDOC],10,11) As [Лицевой счет администратора], [BNV_LINES].[CDOC] As [Номер платежного документа], Coalesce([ZF_D].[SUMM],Case When [BNV_LINES].[DT_CT]=0 Then [BNV_LINES].[SUMM] Else -[BNV_LINES].[SUMM] End) As [Сумма по документу], [K_LS].[CLS] As [Лицевой счет], [K_LS_1].[CLS] As [Лицевой счет по истории], [BNV_LINES].[DATE] As [Дата], [ZF_D].[DBN] As [Дата банка], Max([BNV_LINES].[NPL]) As [Назначение платежа документа] From (((([BNV_LINES] With (NoLock) Inner Join [DOC] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[DOCID]=[DOC].[DOCID])) Left Join [K_LS] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[K_LSID]=[K_LS].[K_LSID])) Left Join [ZF_D] With (NoLock) On ([BNV_LINES].[BNV_LINESID]=[ZF_D].[BNV_LINESID])) Left Join [K_LS] As [K_LS_1] With (NoLock) On ([ZF_D].[K_LSID]=[K_LS_1].[K_LSID])) Where [DOC].[K_TDID]=23 And |0 Group by Convert(DateTime,Left([DOC].[CDOC],8)), Substring([DOC].[CDOC],10,11), [BNV_LINES].[CDOC], Coalesce([ZF_D].[SUMM],Case When [BNV_LINES].[DT_CT]=0 Then [BNV_LINES].[SUMM] Else -[BNV_LINES].[SUMM] End), [K_LS].[CLS], [K_LS_1].[CLS], [BNV_LINES].[DATE], [ZF_D].[DBN] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр разбора информации из расчетных документов
